{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was-- he was really a bit more younger, more friendlier to the children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he explained to us that we are not really Hungarians and we are restricted and we were not-- then I realized it, that our-- the culture of Hungary and the fate of Hungary is-- is not us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hungary is not us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We are something different than the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the earlier years, I was-- I don't know how it worked, but in my mind, I thought this is not contradictory, being Jewish and being Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One is complement each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think this is a most wonderful thing to be a Hungarian Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very proud of the Hungarian history.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also about the Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this doesn't contradict each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- in my childhood, I had-- I thought it a great tragedy what befall our people was that Hungary was-- was taken away territories from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hungary became a [INAUDIBLE] Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were always praying for the resurrection of Great Hungary, which we said it in our prayers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And another thing, that we are in diaspora as Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I hadn't found anything contradictory in these two different terms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's-- it has not came as a shock, because it's not suddenly it came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's somehow-- some-- as one grows older and the situation has changed, then I-- then I gradually, gradually realized the situation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was not, like you put it, a sudden shock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We learned everything, what normal elementary schools study.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, geography, arithmetics, and what's going on-- world history.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was quite-- my favorite subject, always, world history and other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Geography.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very much interested in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was our secular studies.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
